{\b Browser Organizer Host}\par
\par
This installs a small local helper for the Browser Organizer browser extension (Chrome and Edge). The extension uses this helper to run your chosen AI backend (a local AI CLI, or an OpenAI-compatible API) here on your computer and return the results. Your tabs and bookmarks stay on this machine.\par
\par
This is the per-machine installer for administrators: it installs under Program Files and registers the native-messaging host for all users on this computer, so it requires administrator rights. (Individual users who just want it for themselves can use the per-user setup instead.)\par
